Text:
To Fringe einai mia amerikanikh thleoptikh seira episthmonikhs fantasias pou dhmiourghthhke apo ton Tzefrei Tz. Amprams ,
ton Aleks Koyrtzman kai ton Romperto Orki. Anaferetai sto ypotithemeno tmhma paradokswn tou FBI pou vrisketai sth Vostwnh ths Masaxouseths.

H omada pou kaleitai "Fringe Division" vrisketai ypo thn epopteia tou "Ypourgeiou Eswterikhs Asfaleias" (Homeland Security)
kai xrhsimopoiei anorthodokses erevnhtikes texnikes "perithwriakwn" ths episthmhs parallhla me tis klasikes texnikes tou FBI
gia na erevnhsei mia seira apo anekshghta kai polles fores frikiastika peristatika pou sxetizontai me ena mysthriako parallhlo sympan.


H seira anaferetai sthn yparksh enos parallhlou sympantos pros to opoio einai dyskolo na "anoixtei" pylh
kai sto opoio yparxoun sxedon oloi oi "edw" xarakthres alla me elafra diaforetikh ekseliksh.

Enas episthmonas katafere na anoiksei mia pylh kai na perasei se afto metaferontas texnologia pou htan gnwsth "ekei" dhmiourgwntas "edw"
mia panisxyrh etaireia. H pylh afth dhmiourgei arketa provlhmata sto allo sympan kai etsi thewreitai to "edw" sympan ws exthriko
(apo osous vriskontai "ekei" kai ypotithetai oti gnwrizoun thn yparksh tou "edw").
